#: ../pep-0426.txt:665
msgid ""
"The source URL MUST reference either a source archive or a tag or specific "
"commit in an online version control system that permits creation of a "
"suitable VCS checkout. It is intended primarily for integrators that wish to "
"recreate the distribution from the original source form."
msgstr ""

